title: To write from the sqlite shell to a file, use the .output pragma.
pid: bd8eb06f-4ab7-4668-b6a8-6826b0506212
body: |2-
  sqlite> .mode list
  sqlite> .separator |
  sqlite> .output test_file_1.txt
  sqlite> select * from tbl1;
  sqlite> .exit
  $ cat test_file_1.txt
  hello|10
  goodbye|20
  $
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
